                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> One or more creatures within 60 feet of the irradiated undead plant are currently host to at least one seedpod</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The irradiated undead plant pulses with energy, causing the seedpods to sprout vines. Creatures hosting a seedpod must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:16] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes @Damage[1d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes @Damage[2d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 2} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes @Damage[2d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage, is slowed 2 for 1 round, and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Immobilized] until it [[/act escape dc=16]]{Escapes}. Until it Escapes, the creature is a new source of the irradiated undead plant's radioactive remains aura with a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5].</p>"
